title: Hour 1: Tua Taken to hospital
description:
Stephen A., Marcus Spears, Adam Schefter, and Bart Scott dive into the inconsistencies of the NFL's concussion protocol after Tua's injury in last night's game. The crew debates who will shine more on Sunday night: Mahomes or Brady?
